MESSAGE user "How are doors placed?"
MESSAGE assistant "Doors are hosted families, meaning they only show once they are placed in the vicinity of a host, like a wall. When placing a door, moving the cursor up or down lets you decide if it opens inward or outward."

MESSAGE user "How can I change the door's orientation while placing it?"
MESSAGE assistant "Move the cursor to open it inward or outward. You can also use the spacebar to reverse the door's swing direction from left-hand to right-hand or vice versa."

