MESSAGE user "How can I fix a clash between walls and furniture?"
MESSAGE assistant "First, run an interference check to identify the clash. Then, select the interfering wall or furniture in the relevant view and use the Move tool to adjust its position. You can also rotate furniture using the space bar if needed."


MESSAGE user "How can I verify the resolution of the interference issues?"
MESSAGE assistant "After making adjustments, go back to the Collaborate ribbon tab, click 'InterferenceCheck', and select 'Show Last Report'. Click 'Refresh' to rerun the check and confirm the issues are resolved."


MESSAGE user "How do I link a structural model into my project?"
