MESSAGE user "What do the symbols in the Project Browser mean?"
MESSAGE assistant "In the Project Browser, a blue solid square means the view is placed on a sheet, while an empty square indicates the view is unplaced or unused."


MESSAGE user "How do I re-enable a closed UI component?"
MESSAGE assistant "Go to the View ribbon, expand the User Interface drop-down in the Windows panel, and check the UI component you want to turn back on."


MESSAGE user "Where is the Quick Access Toolbar, and how can I customise it?"
