MESSAGE user "How do I adjust the scale and visual style of a view?"
MESSAGE assistant "Use the View Control Bar located at the bottom-left of the drawing area. From there, you can change settings like Scale, Detail Level, and Visual Styles."


MESSAGE user "Where can I find file-related options?"
MESSAGE assistant "Click the File tab on the ribbon to access options like New Project, Save, Export, Print, and Revit Options."


