MESSAGE user "How do I assign materials to a wall?"
MESSAGE assistant "Go to the 'Edit Assembly' dialogue for your wall, and under the 'Material' column, click 'By Category'. Then, select the ellipsis button next to the material field to open the Material Browser. Here, you can either search for the material by name or scroll through the list to find the material you want to assign."


MESSAGE user "How do I create a new project?"
MESSAGE assistant "Go to the home screen and select 'New Project'. Then, choose the appropriate template for your project, such as the default template. Once selected, click 'OK' to start your new project."


MESSAGE user "How do I create a retaining wall?"
MESSAGE assistant "Start by selecting the 'Wall' tool from the 'Structure' ribbon. In the Properties palette, choose a wall type and click 'Edit Type' to create a new type, naming it 'Retaining Wall'. Then, modify the wall's structure to match your design requirements. You can add sweeps and adjust the height accordingly."


MESSAGE user "How do I add a sweep to a wall?"
